errorDescriptions.64:
1. Check if the heat pump evaporator is not covered 
2. Check the cleanliness of the heat pump evaporator 
3. Contact service organization.
errorDescriptions.80:
1. Check the outdoor unit circuit breaker. 
2. Contact service organization.
errorDescriptions.82:
1. Check the heating circuit filter/strainer. 
2. Check the circulation pump of the heat pump circuit. 
3. The temperature in the heating system is too low. 
4. Contact service organization.
errorDescriptions.84:
1. Check the pressure of the heating circuit. 
2. Check the heating circuit filter/strainer. 
3. Check the ball valves of the heat pump circuit. 
4. Check the circulation pump of the heat pump circuit. 
5. Contact service organization.
